snippet.title: Gori: Cuddly Carnage - Exclusive Demo Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description:
Check out the new trailer for the murder-kitty combat game Gori: Cuddly Carnage. Engage in chaotic, bloody battles as adorable yet fierce creatures in a visually striking and fast-paced arena combat game. Gori: Cuddly Carnage is coming to PC at a later date with a demo available now.

#IGN #Gaming
